description.en: Snode is an innovative blockchain-based ecosystem that aims at providing an integrated environment for multiple blockchain-based services. The core value of Snode is masternode solution with a wide range of high quality masternode services. Other services and products introduced in Snode’s Eco System include digital assets, blockchain project support, multi-coin mining pool, etc.
